title: Can't see my year in review
body: I can't see my year in review it just shows the loading circle for 2 seconds then all black screen.

replies.body:
Try using this website instead and let me know if that works better or not ^_^

https://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/year-in-review-2017#/
I also have a black screen in the client. The website works, but I don't get to see the Team Players section to see the friends I do best with.

Do me a favor and try [**clearing your browser history and cookies**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) to see if that helps or not. I'm not 100% sure quite yet what's going wrong, but try to update me if it helps at all or not ^_^!
